gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Not remaining is my self, protection; then speaking with pity, pityful;
Says my mind to me, this is mine own, seeing I am Maya, Brahma, that one. 25

Here are the translations:

Aave nari tano gand jyaare, rahai nahe peete ann tyaaare;
Ati dryv totri tan tyag, vaali ange atyant vaireegya.

Here is the translation:

Tiana ditha adhar pravali, dant dadyam kali rasali;
Sai kahun te shobha mukni, Shobe naasika chanchu shunkni.
